uirements for your next class, those powers would be added to the AA list of powers you could purchase. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unakilosgaremonde.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nakilos Garemonde</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/1/02 12:57:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23061.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Idea for new charactor advancement...</span><hr size=1> I just want them to add quests which result in AA skills. Something reasonably difficult and extensive, but the skill would be great. Excellent RP value, and a really good skill > more stats from items. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31317">Master Nakilos the Illusionist (60 Phantasmist)</a>   <a href="Http://www.keepersofthefaith.org">  &lt;Keepers of the Faith&gt; </a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uavissuprema.showPublicProfile?language=EN>avissuprema</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/3/02 9:18:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23061.topic&index=18>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Idea for new charactor advancement...</span><hr size=1> Veto! No good idea.<br>The big unique special of EQ: its a TEAM GAME. Very specialized classes acting as a team.